			"subclassSource": "TDManiacBerserker",
			"level": 3,
			"page": 1,
			"entries": [
				"对于一些野蛮人来说，愤怒只是实现目标的手段，而目标就是暴力。狂战士之路是一条浸透着无尽暴力的道路。当你进入狂战士的愤怒状态时，你会享受战斗的混乱，不会担心自己的健康或安全。",
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Frenzy|Barbarian||Maniac Berserker|TDManiacBerserker|3|TDManiacBerserker"
				},
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Intimidating Presence|Barbarian||Maniac Berserker|TDManiacBerserker|3|TDManiacBerserker"
				}
			],
			"foundryImg": "icons/weapons/swords/sword-broad-serrated-blue.webp"
		},
		{
			"name": "Frenzy",
			"source": "TDManiacBerserker",
			"className": "Barbarian",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Maniac Berserker",
			"subclassSource": "TDManiacBerserker",
			"level": 3,
			"header": 2,
			"page": 1,
			"entries": [
				"从3级开始，你的鲁莽攻击会将愤怒转化为一种狂暴状态，改变你的思维以寻找暴力。在狂暴状态下，你回合内的所有攻击都可以变成鲁莽攻击，你还可以用额外动作进行一次近战鲁莽攻击。此外，作为进入狂暴状态的额外动作的一部分，你可以使用近战武器进行一次鲁莽攻击。"
			],
			"foundryImg": "icons/skills/wounds/anatomy-organ-heart-red.webp"
		},
		{
			"name": "Intimidating Presence",
			"source": "TDManiacBerserker",
			"className": "Barbarian",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Maniac Berserker",
			"subclassSource": "TDManiacBerserker",
			"level": 3,
			"header": 2,
			"page": 1,
			"entries": [
				"你的伪装和体格 passively 帮助你对他人施加意志，允许你在你的魅力 ({@skill intimidation}) 掷骰上使用你的力量修正。"
			],
			"foundryImg": "icons/creatures/magical/construct-iron-stomping-yellow.webp"
		},
		{
			"name": "Simple Mind",
			"source": "TDManiacBerserker",
			"className": "Barbarian",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Maniac Berserker",
			"subclassSource": "TDManiacBerserker",
			"level": 6,
			"header": 2,
			"page": 1,
			"entries": [
				"在6级时，你在愤怒状态下不能是{@condition charmed}或{@condition frightened}。如果你在进入愤怒状态时是{@condition charmed}或{@condition frightened}，效果将在愤怒持续期间暂停。",
				"此外，如果你受到生物的伤害并且没有激怒，你可以利用你的反应尖叫或疯狂大笑，然后在受到伤害之前进入激怒状态。"
			],
			"foundryImg": "https://i.imgur.com/a8SOGPh.png"
		},
		{
			"name": "Negligent Attack",
			"source": "TDManiacBerserker",
			"className": "Barbarian",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Maniac Berserker",
			"subclassSource": "TDManiacBerserker",
			"level": 10,
			"header": 2,
			"page": 1,
			"entries": [
				"当你使用鲁莽攻击时，你可以投掷一个命中骰来将其作为伤害添加到你的攻击中。此外，如果你发现自己处于{@condition grappled}状态，你可以选择在攻击中解脱而不是使用这个特性造成额外伤害。你可以在短休息中使用这个特性的次数等于你的力量修正值。"
			],
